Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=34}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh boy... - OG}Meu Deus...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:11.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look how much damage they caused. - OG}Eles causaram um estrago enorme.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:17.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Seraphim were all born here, but looks like they didn't hesitate at all. - OG}Mesmo tendo nascido aqui,\Nos Seraphim não pegaram leve...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma explosão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Respond! - OG}Responda!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:30.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi aquela explosão?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Pythagoras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:34.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Respond! - OG}Responda!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:36.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:19.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Prédio C, camsnail 12, escaneie a área.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encontre o Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi um acidente?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espero que ele não tenha sido atingido...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acabei de ver alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:35.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A shadow?! - OG}Uma silhueta?!{PJ}{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The camsnail has been destroyed... - OG}O camsnail foi destruído...{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa coisa quebrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:53.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aonde você vai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou ver o Capacete rapidinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está, Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:04.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee... - OG}Putz...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele sumiu completamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nem sei por onde procurar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, esse lugar é bem grande.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we play hide and seek here, it'll never end. - OG}Se a gente brincasse de esconde-esconde\Naqui, nunca ia acabar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san, what happened? - OG}O que foi, Nami?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gotcha! - OG}Achei!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde?! Onde?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're jewels! - OG}Joias!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! They're not what we're looking for! - OG}Ei! Não é isso que a gente tá procurando!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are these for me? - Polly (Viz?)}Posso ficar com elas?{OG}
Comment: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Jewels!" oughta be followed by{Polly+Camo - alt timing}
Comment: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Wow, so pretty!", not this!{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:41.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"They're jewels!" is most commonly followed by "Beautiful!" - OG}"Joias!" tinha que ser seguido de\N"Que lindo!" Não isso!{Polly+Camo+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá tudo bem, não tá?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're all going to leave the island anyway! - OG}Vocês vão sair da ilha de qualquer jeito!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's take them with us! - OG}Vamos levar com a gente.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's true, but... - OG}{You got a point there, but... - Polly (Viz)}Mesmo que seja verdade...{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is your common sense buggy? - OG}vocês são pirados ou o quê?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's heavy so should we go back? - OG}Tá pesado! Vamos voltar?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We came to search for Stella! - OG}A gente ainda tá procurando a Stella!{Polly+T}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenho escolha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll leave it here, so make sure\Nto lead us here on our way back! - OG}Vou deixar aqui, mas é bom a gente\Nvoltar por esse caminho depois!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:15.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu prometo que volto pra te buscar, meu tesouro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:19.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só pra vocês saberem, esses são\Ndiamantes artificiais pra uso industrial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you make diamonds? - OG}Vocês conseguem fazer diamantes...?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's like a dream! - OG}É um sonho realizado!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What happened to your eyes?! - PP}O que aconteceu com seus olhos?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The future is full of dreams. - OG}O futuro é cheio de sonhos...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{These guys are crazy! - OG}Vocês são malucos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stella! Onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This place is really amazing! - OG}Esse laboratório é incrível mesmo!{Polly+Z+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:42.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's truly a facility that\Nbrings together the best of science. - OG}É realmente o ápice do avanço científico.{Polly+PP+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You got beaten up by Lucci... - OG}O Lucci te deu uma surra mais cedo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But was your face a mask?! - OG}Seu rosto era uma máscara ou algo assim?!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can change your face\Nand appearance as you like! - OG}Eu posso mudar meu rosto\Ne corpo como eu quiser!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:55.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's what the future is like! - OG}Isso é o futuro pra vocês!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where?! Robin! - OG}Onde, Robin?!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um organoide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um órgão artificial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um organoide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's technology vital to the future of medicine! - OG}É uma tecnologia vital pro futuro da medicina!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can make organs?! - OG}Vocês conseguem cultivar órgãos?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's really a stunning technology. - OG}Que tecnologia impressionante.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm relieved. - OG}Enfim, que alívio.{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{this was a piece of\Na dismembered Vegapunk... - OG}isso fosse um pedaço do Vegapunk desmembrado...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, that's too scary! - OG}Isso é assustador demais, para!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Capacete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Edison! This is Shaka! Respond! - OG}Edison, aqui é o Shaka! Responda!{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aconteceu alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't contact anyone. - OG}O rádio não tá funcionando.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, essa coisa, né?
Comment: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:50.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I could hear them until a few minutes ago,\Nbut suddenly, I can't hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:48.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tava ouvindo todo mundo bem\Naté um minuto atrás...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas agora não consigo ouvir nada.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:54.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I don't think I broke it! - OG}Mas tenho certeza que não fui eu que quebrei!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu juro que não fui eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não bati ela em nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The video feeds... - OG}As câmeras...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{are going off one by one. - OG}estão caindo uma por uma.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Someone else is... - OG}Tem alguém aqui...{PP (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:21.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{in the lab. - OG}dentro do laboratório.{PP (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:22.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I never thought I could go on\Na voyage with you one day! - OG}Nunca pensei que navegaríamos juntos,\NSenhora Stussy!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You were at Mom's party, weren't you? - OG}Você estava na festa da Big Mom, não estava?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please call me a dog. - OG}Pode me chamar de seu cachorrinho.{T+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get serious and look for Stella. - OG}Só me ajuda a procurar a Stella.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu bobinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a big laboratory. - OG}Esse laboratório é enorme.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you search every nook\Nand cranny, it'll take forever. - OG}Procurar em cada cantinho\Nvai levar uma eternidade.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:54.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're on a weapons-development floor,\Nso don't set off any shock waves. - OG}Estamos num andar de desenvolvimento de armas,\Nentão não cause nenhuma onda de choque.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:05.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você está, Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Keep looking, York! - OG}Fique atenta, York!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay... - OG}Sim, senhora...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde ele foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we don't leave soon,\Nthe government will catch us. - OG}Se não sairmos logo,\No governo vai nos capturar.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, let's use this! - OG}Então vamos usar isso!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a Bubble Gun! - OG}Isso é uma arma de bolhas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A Bubble Gun?! - OG}Uma arma de bolhas?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cool! - OG}Demais!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right. - OG}Pode crer!{PP}
Comment: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:38.06,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,With this, I can launch a very powerful\Nbubble attack that can deflect anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa belezinha dispara as melhores bolhas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Elas podem rebater qualquer coisa!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You say "deflect" but call it an attack? - OG}Que tipo de ataque só rebate as coisas?{Polly (TCB)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:50.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you can't imagine it,\Ndo you want a demonstration? - OG}Se não consegue imaginar,\Nquer ver em ação?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it really okay?! - OG}Tá falando sério?!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:56.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's made by Vegapunk.\NIt must be an awesome weapon! - OG}If it's made by Vegapunk,\Nthen it must be an awesome weapon!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's made by Vegapunk. - OG}É uma das invenções do Vegapunk!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser uma arma incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're really interested. - OG}Olha só, você tá bem interessado...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Come here! - OG}Ei! Aqui!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? What? - OG}O que foi?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acharam a Stella?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's terrible! - OG}Isso tá feio!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A big explosion must have taken place here! - OG}Parece que teve uma explosão enorme aqui!{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it an enemy?! - OG}Foi um inimigo?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa-whoa-whoa-whoa, what's going on?! - OG}Epa, epa, epa, o que tá acontecendo?!{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Someone's down on the floor! - OG}Tem alguém caído no chão!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, não me diz que é...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, stay with us! - OG}Ei, aguenta aí...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His head is missing! - OG}A cabeça dele sumiu!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que crueldade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His head was blown off! - OG}Arrancaram a cabeça dele?!{PP (Viz-ish)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So this was the explosion we heard earlier! - OG}Deve ter sido a explosão que ouvimos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Pythagoras! Aguenta firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, don't shoot! - OG}Espera, não atira!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me diz que...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A cabeça dele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi um acidente?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:16.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, judging from the situation,\Nwas it an enemy attack?! - OG}Não, pelo que parece,\Nvocê deve ter sido atacado, certo?!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, it's inexplicable! - OG}Mas não faz sentido!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It can't be true... - OG}É difícil de acreditar...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I don't think I was mistaken... - OG}mas tenho certeza que não me enganei...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is it? Just say it! - OG}O que é? Desembucha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is it an error in our design? - OG}Nós cometemos um erro no nosso projeto?{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It really can't be true, but... - OG}Realmente não pode ser verdade, mas...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê a York?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hm?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:43.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Earlier, Edison gave you an order to stop. - OG}O Edison não mandou você recuar mais cedo?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You have to be outside waiting for us. - OG}Você deveria estar lá fora nos esperando.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:50.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're so cute! - OG}Ah, que fofo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{York, what are you doing?! - OG}York, o que você tá aprontando?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:58.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei esse fofinho aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Love-Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Mellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:26.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no! - OG}York!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a seraphim! - OG}Você é um Seraphim!{PP (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop, seraphim! - OG}Pare, Seraphim!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{W... Why are you moving?! - OG}P... Por que você ainda tá se mexendo?!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,W... Why are you moving?!
Comment: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,W... Why are you moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This can't be happening! - OG}Isso não faz sentido!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:04.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I need your help, Luffy! - OG}Me ajuda, Luffy!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são nossos inimigos agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys. - OG}Vocês dois!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop! - OG}Parem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem está comandando vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that how you stop them? - OG}Isso vai fazê-los parar?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They came after CP0, too. - OG}Eles também foram atrás do CP0.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna let these fools die cuffed - OG}Se deixarmos eles morrerem algemados...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{because it'd leave a sour aftertaste. - OG}vai ficar um gosto amargo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:13.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way! - OG}Impossível!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não estão te obedecendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá vendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:28.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She doesn't obey our orders! - OG}Ela não obedece nossas ordens!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hover!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Use seus sapatos de dominação!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso aí!
Comment: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:46.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! - OG}W-Wait, hold on just a–{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! - OG}E-Espera, para um segun–{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh crap! - Polly}Ah, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I caught a glimpse of heaven... - OG}Acho que vi uma luz...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Respond! - OG}Responda!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tá funcionando!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As comunicações caíram!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought she'd obey you! - OG}Parece que a situação mudou!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can I fight back? - OG}Posso revidar?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua pirralha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you kidding me?! - OG}Para de brincadeira!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:28.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She isn't someone you can defeat! - OG}Você não consegue vencer ela!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's our creation... - OG}Nós os criamos pra serem...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The strongest form of humanity! - OG}a forma suprema da humanidade!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a really troubling situation. - OG}Essa é uma situação muito complicada...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não estão seguindo minhas ordens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That means... - OG}O que significa que...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{it's one of the Vegapunks\Nwho is commanding them. - OG}um dos outros Vegapunks\Nestá dando ordens a eles.{T}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What if the communication failure... - OG}A falha na comunicação...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and this situation of\Nbeing trapped in the barrier... - OG}Ficar preso dentro da barreira...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{were all calculated? - OG}E se tudo isso foi calculado?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:27.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que alguém...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,quer nos matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Matar todos nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Malditos Seraphim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Screw them! - OG}Que absurdo!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Straw Hat and Roronoa. - OG}Ei, Chapéu de Palha. Roronoa.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why don't we make a truce... - OG}Que tal fazermos\Numa trégua por um momento...{PP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...e formarmos uma aliança temporária?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se vocês tirarem nossas algemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:01.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,acho que vão nos achar bem úteis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Eles parecem irritados!\N– Eles parecem irritados!{Wano 35 - 02:28}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:17.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's say we uncuff you guys and fight together with you... - OG}Mesmo que a gente tire suas algemas\Ne lute junto com vocês...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:21.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'd just let us cuff you again? - OG}não é como se vocês fossem\Ndeixar a gente algemar de novo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, we will. - OG}Isso não é verdade.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:27.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once we get over the crisis together... - OG}Quando sairmos dessa...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:31.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{we submit to you cuffing us again... - OG}vamos colaborar e deixar vocês nos algemar de novo.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay! Then we'll uncuff you. - OG}Beleza! Fechado.{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Era mentira na cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquilo é...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a técnica do careca?!{"baldy" is from AR 14 - 17:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:03.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Dice-Dice Fruit power! - OG}O poder da Supa Supa no Mi!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give me... food... - OG}Preciso... de comida...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já faz dois meses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{without decent food... - OG}sem uma refeição decente...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente consegue sair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dois meses atrás...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,depois que investigamos Egghead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,nós saímos da ilha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but were attacked by\Nthe weaponized sea beasts... - OG}mas fomos perseguidos\Npelas bestas marinhas armadas...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então voltamos pra ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:57.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os outros agentes da Cipher Pol que vieram\Ninvestigar nosso desaparecimento...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:01.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,acabaram presos aqui também.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:06.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, but I thought\Nyou were the mastermind... - OG}Me desculpe... sempre achei\Nque você era o mentor disso...{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dr. Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't know anything. - OG}Eu não fazia ideia.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I had no idea... - OG}Eu não sabia...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:25.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que isso estava acontecendo em Egghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, céus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It sure was strange... - OG}Acho que {\i1}era{\i0} estranho mesmo...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is no way that\Nresearch on the poneglyphs... - OG}Não tem como nossa pesquisa dos poneglyph...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:39.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{could be leaked to the government. - OG}ter vazado pro governo.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Marine Branch G-9, the ships set out! - OG}Os navios partiram\Nda Base Marinha G-9!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O número de embarcações,\Ngrandes e pequenas, rumo a Egghead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{exceeds 100 now! - OG}agora passa de cem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:55.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have you ever seen his\Ndevil fruit power before? - OG}Você já viu o poder dele antes?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:06.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Baroque Works'... - OG}O cara das lâminas...{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{full-body bladed guy! - OG}da Baroque Works!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que você fez com o Lucci?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixei ele ali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}{Crap! - Camo}Droga!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See?! Roronoa! - OG}Tá vendo, Roronoa?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:48.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you going to keep going to\Nthe trouble of defending us in cuffs?! - OG}Não percebe como é difícil\Nnos defender enquanto estamos algemados?!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,CP0.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Posso perguntar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,qual é a missão de vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All seven Vegapunks'... - OG}A eliminação...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{total elimination. - OG}de todos os sete Vegapunks.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:07.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lucci, how could you say it to his face! - OG}Na cara dele não, Lucci!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And Stussy, who betrayed you guys, - OG}E já que a Stussy traiu vocês...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{won't get off scot-free, right? - OG}ela também tá na mira, certo?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer ela pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:22.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Don't you wanna survive?! - OG}Ei! Cadê seu instinto de sobrevivência?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just run! - OG}Só corre!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami's scream... - OG}Essa foi a Nami com certeza...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There are more than these two in the lab... - OG}Então não são só esses dois.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos os quatro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,estão descontrolados.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We must protect those seven Vegapunks. - OG}Temos que proteger os Vegapunks.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Além disso...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantos mais?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquilo é...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capacete!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The keys to the cuffs. - OG}As chaves das algemas.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll leave it to your judgment. - OG}Vou confiar no seu julgamento.{Camo}
Comment: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to your judgment.
Comment: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:02.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, proteja a Stella a qualquer custo!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Please protect Stella at any cost!
Comment: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Please protect Stella at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim! Pode deixar comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:11.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After we stop all four enemies, - OG}Depois que derrotarmos os quatro...{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you're not gonna lash out at my friends and the Vegapunks just because you can't beat me, right?! - OG}{\q2}você não vai ser mau perdedor e atacar todo mundo\Nsó porque não consegue me vencer, certo?{Polly (TCB-ish)}
Comment: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,you're not gonna lash out...
Comment: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:16.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,at my friends and the Vegapunks just because you can't beat me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You idiot. - OG}Ei, idiota.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That kind of provocation won't work... - OG}Eles não vão cair nesse tipo de provocação...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:23.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course not! - OG}É claro que não!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Because you're the first one I wanna kill! - OG}Você é{\i0} quem eu vou matar primeiro...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:29.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And when you die, - OG}E quando você morrer,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:32.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{all of your friends will die as well! - OG}seus amigos também estão mortos!{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:34.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It worked! - OG}Ele caiu!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:36.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! - OG}Beleza!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is not the time for that! - OG}Agora não é hora pra isso!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:42.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ursus...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:45.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:03.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gear Fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:05.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Boundman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Bonney! - OG}Desculpa, Bonney!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá vou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não atrapalha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:30.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem você pensa que é pra falar assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:36.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Purgatorial Oni Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick: White Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.83,0:23:56.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Six King...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Kong...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:03.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– ...Gun!\N– ...Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.95,0:24:39.04,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Some island in the New World. - OG}{This is a certain island in the New World. - Polly+PP}Em uma certa ilha no Novo Mundo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.75,0:24:46.84,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a bar at a small port. - OG}{we find a bar at a small port. - Polly}{And this is a bar at a small port. - Polly}encontramos um bar em um pequeno porto.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.84,0:24:48.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cheapskate, cheapskate, cheapskate! - OG}Seu idiota!{T+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.01,0:24:51.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tô falando sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.18,0:24:53.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me leva, me leva!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:55.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Take me! - OG}Me leva com você!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:24:57.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{On your next voyage! - OG}Me leva na próxima viagem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.73,0:24:58.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No. - OG}Nem pensar.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.19,0:25:03.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll never take a hot-headed brat like you. - OG}Eu jamais levaria\Num pirralho esquentado como você.{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.82,0:25:08.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desiste logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.95,0:25:11.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our captains will feel bad about this. - OG}Vai chatear nossos capitães!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:12.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No! - OG}De jeito nenhum!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.78,0:25:14.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I admire him! - OG}Eu quero ser igual ao chefe!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.87,0:25:17.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm working on my body, too! - OG}Eu também tô ficando mais forte!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.20,0:25:19.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure I'd be your best crewmember! - OG}Vou ser o melhor da tripulação!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.75,0:25:21.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão se arrepender!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.42,0:25:24.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, say something! You're annoying me! - OG}Ei, fala alguma coisa! Tá me irritando!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.79,0:25:27.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See? You're hot-headed. - OG}Tá vendo? Esquentado.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.01,0:25:28.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, qual é!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.59,0:25:30.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Droga!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.10,0:25:37.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry to interrupt you! - OG}Desculpa interromper!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.77,0:25:38.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.81,0:25:43.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele desgraçado nos atacou!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.15,0:25:48.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our youngsters are out there squabbling,\Nangry about getting blindsided... - OG}Os mais novos estão revidando lá fora,\Nmas tão furiosos por terem sido pegos de surpresa.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.74,0:25:50.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que a gente faz?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.20,0:25:52.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This could turn into a battle! - OG}Isso vai virar uma briga!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.33,0:25:59.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gee... - OG}Caramba...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.20,0:26:01.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know whether it's good or bad timing... - OG}Não sei se o momento\Né bom ou ruim...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.87,0:26:04.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were about to leave... - OG}A gente tava prestes a sair...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.59,0:26:09.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We got carried away talking. - OG}Acho que me empolguei conversando.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.30,0:26:15.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I met some old friends.\NWe both thought the other was dead. - OG}Mas encontrei uns velhos amigos\Ne ambos achávamos que o outro tinha morrido.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:17.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It can't be helped. - OG}Dá pra me culpar?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.14,0:26:20.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure that the enemy is pissed. - OG}Nosso inimigo deve tá furioso.{Polly (Viz-ish)}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.73,0:26:23.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Beck, you can't say that! - OG}Olha quem fala, Beck!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:26.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who do you think he resents?! - OG}Com quem você acha que ele tá bravo?!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.27,0:26:28.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos zarpar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.73,0:26:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are we gonna fight, boss?! - OG}Vamos lutar, Chefe?!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.15,0:26:35.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai ser uma guerra, Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.62,0:26:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vou transformar essa ilha num campo de batalha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.66,0:26:40.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh! He's so cool! - OG}Uau! Ele é tão lindo!{Polly (TCB)}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.37,0:26:45.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to cause major damage here. - OG}Não quero causar nenhum estrago grande aqui.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.79,0:26:50.42,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a proud country of warriors. - OG}Essa é uma terra de guerreiros orgulhosos.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:51.59,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Elbaph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.06,0:27:03.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Could you help us? - OG}Vocês nos ajudariam?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.18,0:27:05.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dorry. Brogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.77,0:27:08.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No problem, bro! - OG}Sem problema, Irmão!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.36,0:27:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai lutar contra eles, Ruivo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.83,0:27:22.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey. Go check with him on one thing first. - OG}{Hey. I need you to\Ncheck something with him first. - Polly+PP}Ei. Vai conferir uma coisa com ele primeiro.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.95,0:27:25.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, with Captain Kid? - OG}Claro, com o Capitão Kid?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.04,0:27:25.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{About what? - OG}O que é?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.92,0:27:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.04,0:27:28.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pergunta isso pra ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.30,0:27:34.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Does he really want to fight me now? - OG}Você realmente quer lutar comigo agora?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.67,0:27:38.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Or does he want to leave the\Nlode poneglyphs behind and go away? - OG}Ou quer largar seus\Nlode poneglyphs e cair fora?{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.39,0:27:40.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tell him to pick one! - OG}Escolha!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.78,0:28:02.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry0}{The few ships visible on the shore, - OG}Os poucos navios visíveis na costa...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.74,0:28:05.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the fools who annoy the hell out of us, - OG}e os que estão atirando preguiçosamente em nós...{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.25,0:28:07.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{are apparently... - OG}são todos...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.87,0:28:12.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...pirates serving under\Nthe Emperor Red Hair's group. - OG}piratas servindo na frota do Imperador Ruivo.{Polly+PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:16.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They seem to be well-known ones. - OG}E parecem ter certa reputação.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.30,0:28:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.55,0:28:23.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I couldn't wait to see you, Chief! - OG}Que bom que voltou, Chefe!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.31,0:28:25.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você também, Beckman!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.73,0:28:29.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stay away from our boss and the others! - OG}Fiquem longe do Chefe e da tripulação!{Polly+Camo+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.06,0:28:31.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to pay you protection money! - OG}Queremos pagar pela proteção!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.90,0:28:34.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't do that! - OG}A gente não faz esse tipo de coisa!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.95,0:28:50.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Before, we didn't even get\Na glimpse of their chief, Red-Hair... - OG}Da última vez, nem conseguimos\Nver o Chefe deles, o Ruivo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.21,0:28:53.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and we still got beaten to a pulp. - OG}e mesmo assim fomos massacrados.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.72,0:29:02.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You even lost one of your arms. - OG}Eles até tiraram um dos seus braços.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.11,0:29:16.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dessa vez, vai ser mais do que só um braço.
